    <arm_group_label>i-gel</arm_group_label>
    <arm_group_type>Experimental</arm_group_type>
    <description>The i-gel is designed to create a non-inflatable anatomical seal of the pharyngeal, laryngeal and perilaryngeal structures whilst avoiding the compression trauma that can occur with inflatable supraglottic airway devices.</description>
  </arm_group>
